---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "../../components/shared/Container.astro";

const articleData = {
  title: "How Canadian E‑Commerce Brands Can Launch a TikTok Shop in the USA",
  category: "Cross‑Border E‑Commerce",
  date: "May 2, 2025",
  readTime: "2 min",
  image: "/images/tiktokcanadaban.webp"
};
---

<Layout title={articleData.title}>
  <article class="pt-[4rem] pb-16 md:pt-[6rem] md:pb-24 bg-body min-h-screen scroll-mt-header">
    <Container>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <img
          src={articleData.image}
          alt={articleData.title}
          class="w-full h-[400px] object-cover rounded-xl shadow-md mb-10" />

        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-heading-1 mb-4">{articleData.title}</h1>
        <p class="text-heading-3 mb-8 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span>{articleData.date}</span><span>•</span><span>{articleData.readTime}</span><span>•</span><span>{articleData.category}</span>
        </p>

        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-heading-2 space-y-12">

          <!-- Intro -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-heading-1 mb-4">Double Your Revenue with TikTok Shop USA</h2>
            <p>
              TikTok Shop USA already processes <strong>billions</strong> in GMV, and early Canadian adopters routinely match their domestic sales within a single quarter. Skipping this market is like leaving cash on the table.
            </p>
            <p>
              The good news? Launching south of the border is easier than you think—especially when LaunchLegit handles the heavy lifting.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-heading-1 mb-4">What It Takes to Launch</h2>
            <p>
              To open a U.S. TikTok Shop you need five essentials: a U.S. LLC, an EIN, a 25 % on‑paper U.S. shareholder, a U.S. bank account, and a verified TikTok Seller Center profile. LaunchLegit delivers each piece as a single, done‑for‑you package—so you spend zero hours on paperwork and 100 % on scaling your brand.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-heading-1 mb-4">Why Waiting Costs You Money</h2>
            <p>
              Every month you delay your U.S. launch, thousands of American shoppers buy from competitors. With TikTok pushing in‑app checkout aggressively, early Canadian brands are already seeing <strong>40‑60 % of their total sales</strong> come from the U.S. channel alone.
            </p>
            <p>
              TikTok’s algorithm favours local inventory and U.S. dollar pricing, so having a U.S.‑verified shop isn’t just “nice to have” — it’s the difference between getting surfaced to American buyers or getting buried.
            </p>
            <p>
              LaunchLegit’s average client timeline is 21 days from signature to first sale. The sooner you start, the sooner you tap a market ten times the size of Canada’s.
            </p>
          </section>

          

          <!-- LaunchLegit CTA -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-heading-1 mb-4">LaunchLegit: Your Turn‑Key U.S. TikTok Shop Partner</h2>
            <p>
              LaunchLegit handles <em>every</em> TikTok Shop requirement for non‑U.S. sellers—nothing outsourced, no hidden fees.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
              <li>Form your U.S. LLC <em>(California / Delaware)</em></li>
              <li>Provide a vetted U.S. local resident shareholder (25 % paper stake, 0 % profit share)</li>
              <li>Draft attorney‑prepared agreements to protect your ownership</li>
              <li>Register and verify your TikTok Shop using the shareholder’s U.S. phone + email</li>
              <li>Open a U.S. bank account for payouts</li>
              <li>Set up a U.S. return address and 3PL connection</li>
              <li>Monthly compliance call &amp; weekly account check‑ins</li>
              <li>Keep all your personal info 100 % confidential</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-6">
              <strong>Ready to go live?</strong> <a href="/#cta" class="text-primary hover:underline">Schedule a free 15‑minute call</a> and we’ll walk you through your launch timeline.
            </p>
          </section>

        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </article>
</Layout>
